.TH item
.SH NAME
item-req
.SH DESCRIPTION
The item requirement specifies the required item for the object.
.SH PARAMETERS
.P
* id
.br
Specifies the ID of required item.
* amount
.br
Specifies the amount of required items.
* charge
.br
Specifies whether the required items should be removed from the object inventory after requirement check.
.SH JSON EXAMPLE
.nf
{
    "id":"item1",
    "amount":1,
    "charge":true
}
.SH XML EXAMPLE
.nf
<item-req id="item1"
	  amount="1"
	  charge="true"/>
.SH SEE ALSO
requirements